responseText: Heya! I don't know if you've noticed, but those goblins turn everything they touch into garbage. We're trying to clean up the ruins, but it feels like every load we haul out is just replaced in an hour by those grabby little beasts. You'll make sure to bring any goblin garbage you find to us, right? We'll throw it in the fire for ya. Busy busy!
name: SQ_NPC_RVR_Batyard_Jackson_1_Response
